<P>These thynges thus done,<NOTE PLACE="marg">The good mynd &amp; fer|uent affeccio~ of y^<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> Author towarde his countrey.</NOTE> I be|gan
