<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">eteste theyr supplicacions. For w^t 
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ut repentaunce, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ayth, and renoua+<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ion
