<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">n y^<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> syght of god. To al such as pray
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">o, God the father by Salomo~ spea|keth
